    <div class="doc-metadata">
        <p><strong>File:</strong> /Documentation/PriorityTodos</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> January 26, 2026</p>
        <p><strong>Author:</strong> System Documentation</p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> Active - Priority Task Management</p>
    </div>

    <details class="overview-section">
        <summary>📋 Overview</summary>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>This document lists priority todos that are blocking critical development progress. Tasks are ordered by their blocking dependencies - resolve items higher on the list first to unblock lower items.</p>
            <p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Dependency-ordered priority list</li>
                <li>Dynamic Daily Task integration via todo/day.tt</li>
                <li>Structured project metadata and tracking</li>
                <li>Action buttons for IDE agent integration</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </details>

