        <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
        <div class="warning-box">
            <h4>Common Issues</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>API returns 401:</strong> Check token validity and Authorization header format.</li>
                <li><strong>Table missing:</strong> Run schema migration to create required tables.</li>
                <li><strong>Dev-only error:</strong> Ensure using comserv_server.pl, not Starman production.</li>
                <li><strong>Schema blocker:</strong> Resolve schema issues before proceeding with Phase 2.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

